<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10104085>
    dc:description "Fig. 10. Male genitalia of Strigister tecolotito. T8 = 8th tergite, S8 = 8th sternite, T9 = 9th tergite, S9 = 9th sternite, T10 = 10th tergite, tg = tegmen, bp = basal piece, ml = median lobe." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10104085/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10104081>
    dc:description "Figs. 3–9. Strigister species. 3) Dorsal habitus of S. tecolotito; 4) Dorsal habitus of S. simoni; 5) Frons of S. tecolotito; 6) Frons of S. simoni; 7) Ventral habitus of S. tecolotito; 8) Pro- and mesosterna of S. simoni; 9) Lateral habitus of S. tecolotito." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10104081/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10104087>
    dc:description "Fig. 11. Map showing collecting localities for the two species of Strigister." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10104087/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

